song.title: Aardvarks agree! (so can we)
song.info:
Cute'sy Synth Pop. Created in 2012.
Instruments: Roland XP30 (synth) Akai MPC1000 (sampler/sequencer) Korg Kaossilator (synth) Audacity for Linux.
No Aardvarks, Indigenous people or University Professors were harmed in the making of this track :-)
